{"tid":1837244,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎殺到 鼠年賀歲盃取消","createTime":"2020-01-23T14:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T14:56:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dda7cfba18073c27f9b02af8e1d17864eb2b82e9","tid":1837244,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:05:59.000Z","msg":"鼠年賀歲盃原定年初二在旺角場上演，但因為武漢肺炎殺入香港，賽事無奈取消。<br />\n<br />\n今次鼠年賀歲盃原定於年初二在旺角場舉行，分別有香港隊在對港聯及香港女子足球代表隊對明日之星隊。不過，由於香港已經有確診的武漢肺炎個案，特區政府宣布取消賽事，免生危險。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=a0e2b3c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"80662d838e6818ed0849d9fcf88c9f1505b65e98","tid":1837244,"uid":179292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"唔睇都擺，本身都冇隊想嚟"},{"pid":"4eac65d8988071a731efbc15ec9a15962c469cea","tid":1837244,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"［行動］文宣向有意到港醫病嘅武漢肺炎病人，引導佢地搵香港警署求助<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837289</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f76868f78dd053682b962f4a6c7a986e187be0ff","tid":1837244,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"希望富力成隊中肺炎"}]}